<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="215">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="215">
In the Northeast of Brazil, the occurrence of this species was recorded for the Caatinga and Cerrado domains (altitude range 60-448 m) (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/00222933.2013.791948" author="Souza, WRM" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Natural History" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" pagination="1 - 10" refId="B76" refString="Souza, WRM, Lima, LRC, Pes, AMO, Pinheiro, U, 2013a. Trichoptera (Insecta) from Pernambuco State, northeastern Brazil. Journal of Natural History 48 (45-46): 1 - 10, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/00222933.2013.791948" title="Trichoptera (Insecta) from Pernambuco State, northeastern Brazil." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/00222933.2013.791948" volume="48" year="2013 a">Souza et al. 2013a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4221.2.1" author="Desiderio, GR" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" pagination="151 - 171" refId="B20" refString="Desiderio, GR, Barcelos-Silva, P, Souza, WD, Pes, AM, Azevedo, CD, 2017. Caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from Maranhao State, Northeast Region, Brazil: A new species, checklist, and new geographical records. Zootaxa 422 (2): 151 - 171, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4221.2.1" title="Caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from Maranhao State, Northeast Region, Brazil: A new species, checklist, and new geographical records." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4221.2.1" volume="422" year="2017">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Desidério">Desiderio</normalizedToken>
et al. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4838.2.6" author="Moreno, LAS" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="215" pagination="257 - 272" refId="B47" refString="Moreno, LAS, Desiderio, GR, Souza, WRM, Lima, LRC, 2020. Updated checklist of caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from the state of Piaui, Northeast Brazil, including a new species and new geographical records. Zootaxa 4838 (2): 257 - 272, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4838.2.6" title="Updated checklist of caddisflies (Insecta: Trichoptera) from the state of Piaui, Northeast Brazil, including a new species and new geographical records." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4838.2.6" volume="4838" year="2020">Moreno et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
